				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$R_{e}$\end{document}Re ratio and the date at which control starts.

The third class of strategy resembles the second, except that instead of targeting a given fraction of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
